(1236, 'nl: DANS, Services', 'This is an overview of the services DANS provides to promote the permanent storage and traceability of research data. For each service, a contact person is mentioned that can provide you with further information.\r\n\r\n&ndash; EASY data archiving and online access to data\r\n&ndash; Persistent Identifiers\r\n&ndash; DANS EASY Online Analysis Tool\r\n&ndash; DANS Data Portal\r\n&ndash; Data Management Plan\r\n&ndash; Datactive -- not found what you were looking for?\r\n&ndash; Access to Statistics Netherlands (CBS) data\r\n&ndash; Access to data from the European data archives collections\r\n&ndash; Access to data and the online learning centre of ICPSR\r\n&ndash; Research &amp; Development\r\n&ndash; Retro-archiving data: the ADA method\r\n&ndash; DANS subsidy for small data projects\r\n&ndash; DANS Symposia\r\n&ndash; Dutch Censuses\r\n&ndash; Dutch Geographic Information System -- NLGis\r\n&ndash; WIVU database Hebrew Old Testament\r\n&ndash; Language and literature services', 13, 0, 'http://www.dans.knaw.nl/en/content/services', 0, 0, 0, '', 0, '2013-04-16 09:06:29', NULL),
(1237, 'nl: DANS, Depositing Data', 'How to deposit data in 7 steps\r\n\r\n1. Prepare your data \r\n2. Got to &lt;link:easy.dans.knaw.nl:EASY&gt;\r\n3. Start the deposit procedure\r\n4. Documentation and access level\r\n5. Upload your data files\r\n6. Submit your data files\r\n7. Publications by DANS', 13, 0, 'http://www.dans.knaw.nl/en/content/data-archive/depositing-data', 0, 0, 0, '', 0, '2013-04-16 09:11:20', NULL),
